    "The total training time for the CNN model is 3180 s, approximately 1 h (53 min).As we can observe in Table 6, the generative AI functions take longer (12.84 s at the worst case) than the troubleshoot- The predictive maintenance analytics function of our customized chatbot HMI classifies the type of fault detected in a factory based on the received system parameters (parameters in Table 5)."
